text: @AOC Seriously?!!! You’re a racist fool! Washington State’s highest death toll was in a nursing home. New Rochelle, NY is mostly white. Hillsborough County, FL is mostly white. The CA deaths were mixed. So exactly how are the COVID-19 deaths mostly brown & black? You’re the RACIST!
